VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT actions\s*=\s*\[\s*"\*"\s*\]
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:"Action":\s*"\*"|actions\s*=\s*\["\*"\]|action\s*=\s*"\*" && MISSING:effect\s*=\s*"Deny"|NotAction|# intentional|# required
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects IAM policies granting all actions via a wildcard (*) permission.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Wildcard IAM Policy Action.
